# Problem-1007

<a href="https://leetcode.com/problems/binary-tree-level-sum/"><img height="30" src="https://img.shields.io/badge/LeetCode-1007-5F75B3?color=blue&style=logo">Binary Tree Level Sum</a>

## Solution

```cpp
class Solution {
public:
    int getSum(TreeNode* root, int level = 0) {
        if (root == nullptr) return 0;
        return root->val + getSum(root->left, level + 1) + getSum(root->right, level + 1);
    }
};
```
### Solution-2

```cpp
class Solution {
public:
    int getSum(TreeNode* root, int level = 0) {
        if (root == nullptr) return 0;
        if (level == 0) return root->val;
        return root->val + getSum(root->left, level - 1) + getSum(root->right, level - 1);
    }
};
```


